# Branch History Tab

## Design refs

- Spec: `Design/branch-history-coding-guide.md`
- Visual mock: `Design/branch-history-v2.jsx`

## Data flow

```
App (tab=history) → request-branch-history { dateRange }
  → extension.loadBranchHistory → getBranchLifecycles()
  → branch-history-data { lifecycles, defaultBranch, remoteMains, window }
  → BranchHistoryTab → execute-branch-action (on success: reload branches/remotes/history/commits)
```

Messages/types in `src/shared/types.ts`: `BranchLifecycle`, `BranchHistoryPayload`, `request-branch-history`, `branch-history-data`, loading scope `branch-history`.

## Git layer (`branch-lifecycle.ts`)

| Helper | Notes |
|--------|-------|
| `resolveDefaultBranch` | `origin/HEAD` → `main` → `master` → first local |
| `resolveHistoryDateWindow` | `presetDays: null` (All) **capped at 90d** — separate from graph date logic |
| `getBranchLifecycles` | local lifecycles + remote-only (`!localBranchName`) |
| `computePerRemoteDivergence` | per-remote `{remote}/{defaultBranch}...branch` behind counts |
| `sortBranchLifecycles` | default → diverged → active → remote-only → merged |

Status algorithm: `branch-status.ts` → `detectStatus`, `generateDescription`, `STALE_THRESHOLD_DAYS = 7`.

## Webview components

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `BranchHistoryTab.tsx` | Summary, legend, selection, detail panel |
| `TimelineSvg.tsx` | Grid, lane layout |
| `BranchLane.tsx` | Label, bar, dots, stale pill |
