## Tests

- `src/test/unit/branch-status.test.ts` — TC-BH01..BH08 + `generateDescription`
- `src/test/unit/branch-lifecycle.test.ts` — TC-BH09..BH13, `getBranchLifecycles` mock integration
- Mock pitfall: `mockResolvedValueOnce` queue leaks across tests — use exact call counts or `mockReset()` in `beforeEach`

## Contextual actions (detail panel)

| Status | Primary action |
|--------|----------------|
| synced | none |
| ahead | Push N |
| behind | Pull N |
| diverged | Push + Pull |
| no-upstream | Set Upstream |
| remote-only | Create Local Branch (pull path) |
